spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:description:
Mi-V RV32IMAF_ L1_ AHB is a softcore 32 bit RISC-V processor with L1 cache and AHB Lite MEM/MMIO Interfaces. Additional feature ECC event monitoring are included.
####Simulation Note#### When simulating this core without CoreJTAGDebug attached, TRST must be tied high. TMS, TDI, TCK must be tied low and TDO must be marked as unused.
